    <string name="helpText">Welcome to the Epidemy game!\nThe rules are simple. The goal is to defeat all other players. This can be achieved by destroying all their crosses or leaving them no move to make. Players make their turns one after another. Each turn the player can make a certain number of moves (3 by default). Each move is a cross or a wall. A cross can be placed on a blank board cell. A wall can be placed on a enemy cross. A move can be made in a board cell that is right next to your cross or to your wall that is connected to your cross directly or through your other walls. You can do nothing with enemy walls but leave them without connection to the enemy crosses.</string>
